similarity.netMHCIIpan <- function(self_filename, foreign_filename, threshold = 4, tcr_contact_weight = 1, other_weight = 0.5){
  self=read.delim(self_filename, stringsAsFactors = FALSE, sep = "", skip=13)
  for (i in c(1,4,6,8,9,11,12,13)){
    self[,i] <- suppressWarnings(as.numeric(self[,i])) #convert columns to numerical (ignore warnings of NA coercion)
  }                                                    #it's not automatically done because there are blank lines
  self <- self[rowSums(is.na(self)) <= 1,]             #clearing lines with more than 1 NAs (all lines have a NA in Exp_Bind column)
  rownames(self)<-NULL
  
  self_top_binders <- self[self$X.Rank_EL<=threshold,]
  self_top_binders <- self_top_binders[order(self_top_binders$X.Rank_BA),]
  
  ## eliminate intersecting peptides
  self_top_binders_nointersect<-self_top_binders
  # 1st iteration
  suppressWarnings(try(for (i in 2:length(self_top_binders_nointersect$Peptide)){
    repeat {for (j in 1:(i-1)){
          if(rownames(self_top_binders_nointersect[i,]) %in% seq(as.numeric(rownames(self_top_binders_nointersect[j,]))-14,as.numeric(rownames(self_top_binders_nointersect[j,]))+14)){
              self_top_binders_nointersect<-self_top_binders_nointersect[-i,]
              break
          }
          }
    if (j == i-1){
      break
    }
    }
  },silent=TRUE))
  # 2nd iteration
  suppressWarnings(try(for (i in 2:length(self_top_binders_nointersect$Peptide)){
    repeat {for (j in 1:(i-1)){
          if(rownames(self_top_binders_nointersect[i,]) %in% seq(as.numeric(rownames(self_top_binders_nointersect[j,]))-14,as.numeric(rownames(self_top_binders_nointersect[j,]))+14)){
              self_top_binders_nointersect<-self_top_binders_nointersect[-i,]
              break
          }
          }
    if (j == i-1){
      break
    }
    }
  },silent=TRUE))
  
  number_of_self_top_binders=dim(self_top_binders_nointersect)[1] #fetch the number of self binders
  
  foreign <- read.delim(foreign_filename, stringsAsFactors = FALSE, sep = "", skip=13)
  for (i in c(1,4,6,8,9,11,12,13)){
    foreign[,i] <- suppressWarnings(as.numeric(foreign[,i]))
  }
  foreign <- foreign[rowSums(is.na(foreign)) <= 1,]
  rownames(foreign)<-NULL
  
  foreign_top_binders <- foreign[foreign$X.Rank_EL<=threshold,]
  foreign_top_binders <- foreign_top_binders[order(foreign_top_binders$X.Rank_BA),]
  
  ## eliminate intersecting peptides
  foreign_top_binders_nointersect<-foreign_top_binders
  # 1st iteration
  suppressWarnings(try(for (i in 2:length(foreign_top_binders_nointersect$Peptide)){
    repeat {for (j in 1:(i-1)){
          if(rownames(foreign_top_binders_nointersect[i,]) %in% seq(as.numeric(rownames(foreign_top_binders_nointersect[j,]))-14,as.numeric(rownames(foreign_top_binders_nointersect[j,]))+14)){
              foreign_top_binders_nointersect<-foreign_top_binders_nointersect[-i,]
              break
          }
          }
    if (j == i-1){
      break
    }
    }
  },silent=TRUE))
  # 2nd iteration
  suppressWarnings(try(for (i in 2:length(foreign_top_binders_nointersect$Peptide)){
    repeat {for (j in 1:(i-1)){
          if(rownames(foreign_top_binders_nointersect[i,]) %in% seq(as.numeric(rownames(foreign_top_binders_nointersect[j,]))-14,as.numeric(rownames(foreign_top_binders_nointersect[j,]))+14)){
              foreign_top_binders_nointersect<-foreign_top_binders_nointersect[-i,]
              break
          }
          }
    if (j == i-1){
      break
    }
    }
  },silent=TRUE))
  
  foreign_top_binders_nointersect<-foreign_top_binders_nointersect[!duplicated(foreign_top_binders_nointersect$Core),]
  number_of_foreign_top_binders=dim(foreign_top_binders_nointersect)[1] #fetch the number of foreign binders
  
  core_length <- nchar (foreign_top_binders_nointersect$Core[1]) #fetch core length of binders
  table_compiled <- c()
  
  pmbec <- read.table("~/Documents/TTP/script/PMBEC.txt")
  
  for (i in 1:number_of_self_top_binders){
    CR_score <- c(rep(-100,5))
    foreign_core <- c(rep("x",5))
    foreign_sp <- rep(sub('\\_.*$', '', basename(foreign_filename)),5)
    foreign_prot <- c(rep("x",5))
    foreign_pos <- c(rep(1,5))
    self_core <- rep(self_top_binders_nointersect$Core[i],5)
    self_pos <- rep(self_top_binders_nointersect$Pos[i],5)
    table_per_self_peptide <- data.frame(self_core,foreign_core,CR_score,self_pos,foreign_sp,foreign_prot,foreign_pos,stringsAsFactors = FALSE)
    str1 <- str_split(self_top_binders_nointersect$Core[i], "")[[1]] #splitting self binders to individual residue
    for (j in 1:number_of_foreign_top_binders){
      result <- c() #tcr contact residues score for each foreign binder
      str2 <- str_split(foreign_top_binders_nointersect$Core[j], "")[[1]] #splitting foreign binders to individual residue
      for (k in 1:core_length){
        if (k %in% c(2,3,5,8)){
          result <- c(result,tcr_contact_weight*pmbec[str1[k],str2[k]]/pmbec[str1[k],str1[k]])
        } else {
          result <- c(result,other_weight*pmbec[str1[k],str2[k]]/pmbec[str1[k],str1[k]])
        }
      }
      if (sum(result) > table_per_self_peptide$CR_score[5]){
        table_per_self_peptide$CR_score[5] <- sum(result)
        table_per_self_peptide$foreign_core[5] <- foreign_top_binders_nointersect$Core[j]
        table_per_self_peptide$foreign_prot[5] <- foreign_top_binders_nointersect$Identity[j]
        table_per_self_peptide$foreign_pos[5] <- foreign_top_binders_nointersect$Pos[j]
        table_per_self_peptide <- table_per_self_peptide[order(table_per_self_peptide$CR_score,decreasing=TRUE),]
      }
    }
    table_compiled<-rbind(table_compiled,table_per_self_peptide)
  }
  
  table_compiled<-table_compiled[order(table_compiled$CR_score,decreasing=TRUE),]
  
  output_name <- paste0("result_",sub('\\_.*$', '', basename(self_filename)),"_",tools::file_path_sans_ext(basename(foreign_filename)),"_",threshold,"_",tcr_contact_weight,"_",other_weight,"_netMHCIIpan")
  assign(output_name, head(table_compiled,5), envir = .GlobalEnv)
}
